    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the robust 3.8L DFI flat-six powerplant. This specimen is mechanically flawless, delivering 385 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), ensuring optimal damping and razor-sharp turn-in. This vehicle boasts zero bore scoring concerns typical of earlier M96/M97 units and retains its factory-original cross-drilled rotors with ample pad life. The Sport Exhaust (PSE) provides a visceral acoustic profile across the rev range. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the undercarriage is free of oxidation or fluid seepage. A purist\u2019s configuration in truly concours-ready condition.",
